if {Quincy.book_too_early} == false:
	Theo (Concerned): Dalton!?
	Theo (Awkward): Where did you go?
	Dalton (Resting): I'm upstairs.
	Theo (Thinking): Why?
	Theo (Talk): We still haven't finished down here.
	Dalton (Sigh): Huuh...
	Quincy (Laugh): Hah.
	Quincy (Default): Seems like your little doggy partner needs some help.
	set {Quincy.book_too_early} = true
else:
	Theo (Concerned): Dalton!?
	Dalton (Sigh): Yeah...
	Dalton (Resting): Coming.
